### 1) 基础 GET 请求测试
GET http://localhost:8080/
Accept: application/json

### 2) 带认证 Cookie 的 GET 检查
GET http://localhost:8080/auth/check
Accept: application/json
Cookie: access_token={{access_token}}

### 3) 登录（验证码）并写入 Cookie
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/login?code={{code}}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4) 刷新令牌（支持 Cookie 与 Authorization）
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/refresh
Accept: application/json
Cookie: refresh_token={{refresh_token}}

### 5) 跨域 CORS 测试（模拟浏览器预检）
OPTIONS http://localhost:8080/admin/login?code=0000
Origin: http://localhost:5173
Access-Control-Request-Method: POST
Access-Control-Request-Headers: content-type,x-xsrf-token

### 6) 跨域带 Cookie 的 POST（需服务器允许并开启 withCredentials）
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/login?code={{code}}
Origin: http://localhost:5173
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: XSRF-TOKEN={{xsrf_token}}; access_token={{access_token}}; refresh_token={{refresh_token}}
X-XSRF-TOKEN: {{xsrf_token}}

{
  "account": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}
